<h1>Hello <%= @resource.name %>!</h1>

<p>Someone has invited you to <%= external_domain_link(root_path) %>, you can accept it through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Accept invitation', external_domain_link(accept_invitation_path(@resource, :invitation_token => @resource.invitation_token)) %></p>

<p>If you don't want to accept the invitation, please ignore this email.<br />
Your account won't be created until you access the link above and set your password.</p>